AUTOMATED:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=06FeTFN-Uv4   - AUTOMATED using Reflector and Archfi

pacman -S reflector

pacman -Syyy

pacman -S reflector

reflector -c 'United States' --sort rate --save /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist

wget archfi.sf.net/archfi

sh archfi

*set Language - en_US

*set keyboard US - down

*set disk auto partition GPT

*skip enable dhcpd - since kde will use networkmanager

*use trizen or yay

*continue with the options then install favourite DE






